@startuml
title AD_06 Delete Ticket - Activity

' Limitation: explicit delete operation is not available in class_diagrams; close is used as supported equivalent.
start
:Admin selects ticket to remove from active queue;
if (Ticket eligible for removal?) then (Yes)
  :Close ticket;
  :Hide from active ticket list;
  stop
else (No)
  :Keep ticket open;
  stop
endif

@enduml
